data.description: Brand New Stonehollow Home! Impressive curb appeal with 8ft Front door with speakeasy, Alpine Fog Brick, & Barn style Garage doors. Designer Wood-style Tile flows from the spacious Entry into the front Study with french doors, & thru the Formal dining, Kitchen, Cafe, & Family rm with full stone gas starter fireplace. The open gourmet kitchen has 42in white with chocolate glazed painted cabinets, a travertine backsplash, double ovens, cooktop with drawers, & an island with white porcelain farmhouse sink. Granite countertops in kitchen and all baths. Master suite has oversized shower with dbl bench & 2 large walk-in closets. Upstairs is 3 beds, 2 full baths, Media room with 2 levels & game rm & the list goes on!
